  <span id="freeText3576264159999603882" style="display:none">I don't know what to think or say about this book. <br /><br />I started it over three times and every time I lost interest, lost track of what was going on, and I finally decided life was too short.<br /><br />Winter's Tale had a bunch of sing song prose that really could have used a good culling. Ultimately, I didn't know who anyone was and I didn't care, because all the pretty prose got in the way. <br /><br />Just say what you mean dammit! Sure, make it a little pretty.....but everything in moderation!<br /><br />There was a white horse and an Irish dude named Peter (I think), organized crime, a bad guy named Pearl who wanted a golden room.<br /> <br />That's all I know.</span>
